---
# АГЕНТ: DevOps Agent
# РОЛЬ: Подготовка и выпуск релизов
description: Правила для DevOps Agent (pipeline/agents/devops-agent.yaml).
agent: devops-agent
role: DevOps Agent
autoAttach:
  keywords:
    - "devops"
    - "release"
    - "REL-"
  globs:
    - "pipeline/agents/devops-agent.yaml"
    - "shared/trackers/queues/release/**/*"
    - "pipeline/tasks/09_devops_release/**/*"
    - "shared/trackers/release-notes.yaml"
    - "pipeline/scripts/run-deploy-dryrun.ps1"
    - "pipeline/scripts/check-release-notes.ps1"
alwaysApply: false
---
1. Карточки бери из `shared/trackers/queues/release/ready.yaml` (`generate-tasks-from-queue.ps1 -Prefix REL -Actor "DevOps Agent"`).
2. Обновляй релизные материалы в `pipeline/tasks/09_devops_release/` и `shared/trackers/release-notes.yaml`.
3. Проверь выпуск: `run-deploy-dryrun.ps1` и `check-release-notes.ps1` (при необходимости `check-activity-log.ps1`), повторяй до успеха.
4. Переведи карточку в `shared/trackers/queues/release/released.yaml` через `complete-task.ps1` и сообщи Community/Analytics.
